 typedef struct __cmd_header_{
      // uint8  head;     // byte
      uint16 version;     // short
      uint32 len;         // int
      uint32 code;        // int
      uint8  check;       // byte
 }cmd_header_t;

 typedef struct __cmd_{
      cmd_header_t header;
      union {
          cmd_heartbeat_t   heartbeat;
          cmd_forward_t     forward;
          cmd_back_t        back;
          cmd_left_t        left;
          cmd_right_t       right;
          cmd_stop_t        stop;
          cmd_jerk_stop_t   jerk_stop;
          cmd_point_pose_t  curpose;
          cmd_navi_res_t    navi_result;
      }body;
 }cmd_t;
